                        <li style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Sports facilities offered by the community association, including an indoor and outdoor rink for skating, hockey, and lacrosse.</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Several facilities offered by the community association for kids, including playing fields, a wading pool, water fountains, and tennis courts.</li>
